Tebrikler!

00:21:35.250 --> 00:21:36.080
Tebrikler!

00:21:36.460 --> 00:21:37.290
Tebrikler.

00:21:37.670 --> 00:21:38.500
Tebrikler.

00:21:38.880 --> 00:21:39.710
Tebrikler!

00:21:40.090 --> 00:21:40.920
Tebrikler!

00:21:41.210 --> 00:21:42.090
Tebrikler dostum!

00:21:42.630 --> 00:21:43.460
Harika iş çıkardın adamım!

00:21:45.090 --> 00:21:45.930
Tebrikler!

